{"tid":2347760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"(唔畀香港人走?)駐港部隊組織聯合海空巡邏防非法外逃","createTime":"2020-12-31T09:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T09:59:57.000Z","uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3b02e006c75913db92bb6778742f536bb9cdbf47","tid":2347760,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"駐香港部隊在其微信公眾號表示，組織聯合海空巡邏，檢驗部隊履行防務能力。<br />\n<br />\n海軍4艘艦艇與空軍2架直升機快速出動，在香港附近海域進行警戒，防止「恐怖分子」從海上乘船外逃。<br />\n<br />\n在香港的下尾灣海域，駐香港部隊參演部隊發現了一艘模擬可疑船隻，正在朝外海方向高速行駛，接到聯合查證命令後，任務部隊快速判明目標屬性，並進行喊話警告。<br />\n<br />\n對可疑船隻進行攔截查證後，海軍艦艇羈押引導該船向錨地航行。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/articlePrint/id/2674437\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2FarticlePrint%2Fid%2F2674437&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=48a5e01e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/articlePrint/id/2674437</a>"},{"pid":"54a80a4b0aa4cfab50a5cf1bfcbd7a12c27719ec","tid":2347760,"uid":274720,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:32:34.000Z","msg":"1. 殺雞用牛刀<br />\n2. 有恐怖分子係境內，處理方法係等佢地外逃"},{"pid":"4d87f69c3ef080d79c5caccfc763cec1c2e3447a","tid":2347760,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:33:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4bbfa05d967ea8e417222fd156d68bcd9bfb3a7","tid":2347760,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:34:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c502326364c80ee2de4710cc8cc5ca9bb47e1e35","tid":2347760,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:35:51.000Z","msg":"一架MQ9 準備變肉醬